import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { DataService } from '../data.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-retailers', templateUrl: './retailers.component.html', styleUrls: ['./retailers.component.scss'] }) export class RetailersComponent implements OnInit { data: any; constructor(private dataService: DataService) {} ngOnInit() { this.dataService.getData().subscribe(response => { this.data = response; console.log(this.data); }); } }
